{"tid":1565562,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"10月5日，我地一齊入新屋嶺探訪義士","createTime":"2019-09-13T07:56:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T05:27:36.000Z","uid":73783,"like":26,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4493f15c7adce9db26d89eea0fee6fedb318fa11","tid":1565562,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T07:56:47.000Z","msg":"新屋嶺入面發生咩事<br />\n到而家都係一個謎<br />\n點解連太平紳士都入唔到去<br />\n有冇人被強姦，義士們受到何等對待<br />\n我地冇一個人清楚真相<br />\n再說，任何一個被捕人士都有被探訪權<br />\n要確保佢地有冇事<br />\n但佢地而家連律師都唔俾見<br />\n電話被沒收<br />\n同外面失去聯絡<br />\n<br />\n我地要確保義士們既人權得到保障<br />\n要見到義士，同佢地交談<br />\n了解入面發生咩事<br />\n唔可以在入面建立一個新彊集中營<br />\n我知，好多人都話無可能入到去<br />\n我都咁樣認為<br />\n但至少，我地可以raise到public awareness<br />\n讓更多人好奇入面發生既事<br />\n要求警方作個交代<br />\n至少，令到佢地唔敢咁放肆<br />\n<br />\n所以，我懇求大家<br />\n10月5同我地一齊站出黎<br />\n要求探訪新屋嶺被捕人士<br />\n佢地為我地做左咁多<br />\n絕唔係condom<br />\n我地為佢冒少少風險<br />\n又驚咩<br />\n<br />\n10月5，大家見"},{"pid":"fccc0146aef7fb01018de9e942dfe05b7ffa95ba","tid":1565562,"uid":73783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:00:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06cc33f10eae084a1be9678e72ef450d2a7669f9","tid":1565562,"uid":4050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:17:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">請不要再討論唱歌跳閘，實事派請全面進場。</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"4d88bb257f16dc6cde01d6076dfc7a0918224b4c","tid":1565562,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:21:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>915去完英領去民陣遊行！升級玩國際戰線！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋升級玩國際戰線！繼續遍地開花！每個星期去唔同領事館，舉唔同國旗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1559803/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBbo7qE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBbo7qE.jpg&h=5a962f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQY3pQn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQY3pQn.jpg&h=1db04e57&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c0b8613385e6c3ee7eb7491f9230850ae55b0b3c","tid":1565562,"uid":6435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T08:21:47.000Z","msg":"見呢排拉少左人想叫人入去自動送頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f54b07164ab3bcffb46bcde4192b803ed4ac52","tid":1565562,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:20:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"027889686c8bef127736c899c1a312754719f7a6","tid":1565562,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:24:55.000Z","msg":"好，我想去"},{"pid":"c69435fcc33007fef87384584aa1408230644b83","tid":1565562,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:30:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24470900e9ce5e5069efb691257980e5dca30dad","tid":1565562,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T10:31:09.000Z","msg":"屌，冇人推"},{"pid":"3b83f3b4becc935a5be7d15cb8f3f9750edcaba1","tid":1565562,"uid":41963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-13